OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMacKenzie Scott donates    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F$640m to US non-profits    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, MacKenzie Scott, the ex-wife of Amazon 
OL,6, founder Jeff Bezos, is giving $640m    
OL,7, (#504m) to non-profit organisations,   
OL,8, more than double her previously planned
OL,9, donations for the year.                
OL,11,FThe billionaire announced this week she
OL,12,Fwould give the money to 361 small      
OL,13,Fgroups, out of the more than 6,000     
OL,14,Forganisations that applied for funding.
OL,16,FShe had initially planned to make 250  
OL,17,Fawards of $1m each this year.          
OL,19,FMs Scott has given away $16.5b since   
OL,20,Fdivorcing Mr Bezos in 2019.            
